13
00:02:05,170 --> 00:02:06,660
Thank you very much!

14
00:02:06,660 --> 00:02:08,460
Throw me sometime, will you?

15
00:02:08,460 --> 00:02:10,020
What did you just say?

16
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:11,940
Still...</i>

17
00:02:12,860 --> 00:02:15,690
What happened to Assistant Manager Hagoromo?</i>

